      <title>中国取消刺激出口的税收优惠措施 铝价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/metals-suffer-bruising-week-on-strong-dollar-china-demand-woes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[铝价周五上涨，此前中国宣布将取消一项有助于推动数十年来出口繁荣并保护产能过剩行业的退税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-15/metals-suffer-bruising-week-on-strong-dollar-china-demand-woes</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Nov 2024 04:21:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储暗示不会急于降息，黄金迎来 2021 年以来最糟糕的一周</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/gold-holds-near-two-month-low-as-powell-flags-rate-cut-restraint</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员降低对美联储下个月降息的预期，金价交易价格接近两个月低点，有望创下自 2021 年 6 月以来最糟糕的一周。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/gold-holds-near-two-month-low-as-powell-flags-rate-cut-restraint</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 23:34:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>地缘政治降温导致油价周五下跌，油价结束短暂上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-15</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易商利用俄罗斯与乌克兰紧张局势降温的迹象，为未来几个月市场供应过剩局面做准备，导致油价结束了连续三天的反弹行情。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-15</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 23:33:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
